    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should see someone but i'm honestly super busy with work this week and an appointment is gonna take forever. it's probably just an irritation since i've been using my screen so much. if i just use the lubricating drops like i suggested, is there any reason that would be bad? like, wouldn't it just help soothe the redness while it clears up on its own?",
